<template>
	<canvas canvas-id="canvasArcbar1" id="canvasArcbar1" class="charts3"></canvas>	
</template>

<script>
    import uCharts from './u-charts.js';
    var _self;
    var canvaArcbar1;
    export default{
        data() {
        return {
            cWidth3:'',//圆弧进度图
				cHeight3:'',//圆弧进度图
				arcbarWidth:'',//圆弧进度图，进度条宽度,此设置可使各端宽度一致
				pixelRatio:1,
				textarea:''
            }   
        },
        mounted() {
			_self = this;
            this.cWidth3='250'
			this.cHeight3='250'/这里要与样式的宽高对应
			this.arcbarWidth='24'
        }
    }  
</script>
<style>
	/*样式的width和height一定要与定义的cWidth和cHeight相对应*/
	.charts{
        width: 750upx; 
        height:500upx;
        background-color: #FFFFFF;
    }
</style>
